{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "07", "m": "07", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "01", "M": "55", "S": "49"}}, "news": [{"title": "Spain, Portugal step up scrutiny of soaring property markets", "para": "Spain and Portugal are closely watching their booming property markets, which show early signs of overheating with significant price hikes and strong mortgage lending. While regulators are introducing minor cooling measures, like adjusting debt-to-income ratios in Portugal, heavy intervention is unlikely. Current market conditions, though robust, are not mirroring the pre-2008 boom, with analysts suggesting supply constraints and a strong economy are driving current price growth.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/spain-and-portugal-monitor-surging-property-prices-amid-economic-growth/132216671?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-408418/132216671.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "international"}, {"title": "Gillco Group to invest \u20b9800 crore to develop 12-acre housing project in Mohali", "para": "Gillco Group will invest about \u20b9700-800 crore to develop Gillco Meraqui, a 12-acre residential project in Sector 126, Mohali. The project will comprise 444 apartments, with total revenue potential estimated at \u20b92,300-2,400 crore.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/gillco-group-announces-800-crore-investment-in-luxury-housing-project-in-mohali/132221220?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-2001930/132221220.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "India office leasing hits 24.6 million sq ft in Q2 2026: Report", "para": "India\u2019s office market recorded gross leasing of about 24.6 million sq ft in Q2 2026, the highest quarterly absorption on record, according to CBRE. New completion